member.returns:
A collection of  objects containing the found data,
where each  contains all the data for the corresponding dimension;
or an empty collection if there is no data for .

member.summary:
Returns a deep copy of the graph scales. This can return null to exclude an
axis or non-axis scale. For copying, any propery can be changed or copied;
at the very least, any dependency object derived items from the parent axis must be null.

